quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  16,10,Ndivo (Allah) vanonaisa mvura kubva kudenga; kubva mairi munomwa uye zvirimwa (zvinokura) zvamunozotumira zvipfuwo zvenyu kunofura
  16,11,"Vanokumereserai nemvura iyoyo zvirimwa nemaOrivhi (Zaitoon), nemadheti, nemagirepi, uye nemichero yese. Zvirokwazvo, mune izvi mune chiratidzo kune vanhu vanofunga"
  16,12,"Uye vakakugadzikirai usiku nesikati, uye zuva nemwedzi, uye vakagadzika nyenyedzi nemurawo wavo. Zvirokwazvo, mune izvi mune chiratidzo kune vanhu vanonzwisisa"
  16,13,"Uye vakakusikirai zvese pano pasi zvine ndarama dzakasiyana-siyana. Zvirokwazvo, mune izvi mune chiratidzo kune vanhu vanorangarira"
  16,14,"Uye ndivo vakakugadzikirai gungwa, kuti muve munodya kubva mariri nyama nhete nyoro (hove), uye kuti muve munoburitsa kubva mariri zvinemo zvekupfeka. Uye unoona ngarava dzichifamba mariri, kuti muve munotsvaga makomborero avo, uye kuti muve munotenda"
  16,15,"Uye vakagadzika panyika makomo akamira zvakabata, kuti zvimwe ingabvunde nemi; uye nzizi nenzira, kuti muve munotungamirirwa"
  16,16,Uye zviratidzo (masikati) uye nenyenyedzi (husiku) munozvitungamirira
  16,17,Vakafanana here vanosika neuyo asingasiki? Hamurangariri here
  16,18,"Uye mukada kuverenga makomborero aAllah, hamukwanisi kumaverenga. Zvirokwazvo, Allah vanoregerera zvikuru, vane tsitsi zhinji"
  16,19,Uye Allah vanoziva zvamunovanza nezvamunoburitsa
  16,20,"Avo (vanosanganisa Allah nezvimwe zvinhu) vavanokumbira kunze kwaAllah, havana kana chavakasika, asi ivo zvisikwa (vakasikwa)"
  16,21,"Zvitunha, havasi vapenyu, uye havazivi kuti vachamutswa rinhi"